--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.4.3 (2018-04-24)
I: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.4.2 (2018-04-14)
I: Relocate 'PermitRootLogin' parameter

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-04-10)
I: Improve 'Ciphers', 'HostKeyAlgorithms', 'KexAlgorithms' and 'MACs' defaults

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-04-09)
F: Add option to define HostKeyAlgorithms

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-13)
I: Allow additional key exchange algorithms and message authentication codes

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-01-10)
I: Improve Jinja2 filters

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-05)
F: Initial release
